{"tid":211012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[長篇][魔幻][腦洞]《光痕》(Remains of Light)","createTime":"2017-04-21T10:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T10:42:33.000Z","uid":107948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a1afb4d9c6fc6e390aa0e25dd24a372deb55eec","tid":211012,"uid":107948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"第一次Post文，不太熟悉連登的環境，請大家多多指教。<br />\n本小說純熟腦洞，與本人的經歷沒甚麼關係，其中涉及一些對科學、宗教的淺見，不知正確不正確，概念有誤的話，請大家盡管批評，我會改的。<br />\n<br />\n簡介:<br />\n201X年。香港。 <br />\n文青水月，奮身投入學生會的濁流，卻遭好友背叛而引退。<br />\n心情低迷的雨夜，在旺角邂逅神秘少女艾絲琳。 <br />\n虛與實、科學與魔法、神與魔、瘋狂與理性，一切的一切，在這個彈丸之地迸發出燎原的火星&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n「光照在黑暗裡，黑暗卻不接受光。這就是我的故事，光的故事。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/147V15S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F147V15S.jpg&h=6c23c6f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紙言Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/article/96849/%E5%85%89%E7%97%95-%28Remains-of-Light%29.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticle%2F96849%2F%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%2597%2595-%2528Remains-of-Light%2529.html&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6c428c9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/article/96849/%E5%85%89%E7%97%95-%28Remains-of-Light%29.html</a>"},{"pid":"b945beeca903d80e2b92652926c8338b63a60ec9","tid":211012,"uid":107948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"呃，好像post錯區了，我去講故台"}]}